{
  "stem": "6257.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were his parents and the very-- his very young sister who was my age or a little younger even.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Suddenly there was a Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were-- seemed terribly Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't even speak Polish particularly well, the parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they burned candles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It just made, you know, such a different experience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they were in one of the cellars during the uprising as well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Well, I suppose I was given food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and we used to go and fetch water from the Vistula.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Out of the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When things were-- got a bit quiet, I suppose when you-- yes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember that, except that eventually I saw a lot of killed people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At first, it seemed very exciting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it meant that we had lost contact with [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Vladka ?] and all this-- and the sort of underground.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because when the Germans got-- they evacuated everyone from that bit of Warsaw where I was and took us all to outside walls that were sort of some big church where they did some kind of selecting, taking the younger men and some women to work in Germany.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I remember being in that church, where I sort of come to realize that-- I also remembered the conditions, in a way, in-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's how it seemed rather similar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People were so terrified.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were no lavatories and-- in this church.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And people were behaving so badly from-- looking for a room for each other, which I-- because I used to-- but, you know, some people behaved terribly well.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, people were pushing really to sit down.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
